```class Solution {
    public List<Integer> lexicalOrder(int n) {
        List<Integer> res = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
            if (i <= 9) res.add(i);
            else {
                int j = i;
                while (j > 9) j /= 10;
                while (j > 1) {
                    res.add(i);
                    j--;
                }
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
